#: ../../contributors_manual/user_support.rst:38
msgid "Tablet Support"
msgstr "繪圖板、數位板支援"

#: ../../contributors_manual/user_support.rst:40
msgid ""
"The majority of help requests are about pen pressure and tablet support in "
"general."
msgstr "最常見的使用者求助個案是關於數位板筆壓感應與其他數位板問題。"

#: ../../contributors_manual/user_support.rst:44
msgid "Quick solutions"
msgstr "快捷解決方法"

#: ../../contributors_manual/user_support.rst:48
msgid ""
"With every change mentioned below you might need to restart your PC to see "
"the effect."
msgstr "套用以下提到的變更操作之後，可能需要重新啟動電腦才會生效。"

#: ../../contributors_manual/user_support.rst:50
msgid "*For Windows, all devices:*"
msgstr "*針對所有運行 Windows 的裝置：*"

#: ../../contributors_manual/user_support.rst:52
msgid ""
"Change API in :menuselection:`Settings --> Configure Krita... --> Tablet "
"Settings`."
msgstr "到\\ :menuselection:`設定 --> 設定 Krita… --> 數位板設定`\\ 版面更改數位板輸入 API。"

#: ../../contributors_manual/user_support.rst:54
msgid ""
"Wintab: older standard; it supports multiple buttons and high number of "
"pressure levels. If it works fine for you, don't change to Windows Ink. 2-"
"in-1 devices by default use Windows Ink, you can get a Wintab driver but you "
"need to install it separately."
msgstr ""
"WinTab：舊式數位板 API 標準。它支援多於一個數位筆按鍵和較高的筆壓等級數目。如果這能正常運作，沒有特殊理由的話不應切換到 Windows "
"Ink。二合一平板電腦預設使用 Windows Ink。部分硬體廠商有提供 WinTab 驅動程式，但一般要手動安裝。"

#: ../../contributors_manual/user_support.rst:56
msgid ""
"Windows 8+ Pointer (Windows Ink): newer standard; it cuts the pressure "
"levels to 1024. It is more suitable for 2-in-1 devices like Surface Pro and "
"Yoga. Some less known brands might not have this standard implemented."
msgstr ""
"Windows 8+ 指標輸入 (Windows Ink)：較新的 API 標準。這個 API 只支援 1024 級筆壓。這比較適用於二合一平板電腦。"
"某些較冷門的數位板品牌可能未有提供這個 API。"

#: ../../contributors_manual/user_support.rst:58
msgid "*For Windows, tablet/digitizer devices (not convertible/2-in-1 ones):*"
msgstr "*針對在 Windows 使用外接式數位板裝置（非二合一平板電腦）：*"

#: ../../contributors_manual/user_support.rst:60
msgid ""
"Reinstall your driver (Windows Update often breaks tablet driver settings, "
"reinstallation helps)."
msgstr "重新安裝驅動程式（Windows Update 經常會損壞數位板驅動程式的設定，重新安裝會有幫助）。"

#: ../../contributors_manual/user_support.rst:62
msgid ""
"*Wacom tablets:* if you get straight lines at the beginnings of the strokes, "
"first try to update your driver: it should be fixed in 6.3.34-3. If it "
"doesn't work, disable/minimize \"double-click distance\" in Wacom settings."
msgstr ""
"*Wacom 數位板：*\\ 如果在起筆時出現直線線段，請先嘗試更新驅動程式。這個問題應該已在驅動程式版本 6.3.34-3 中修正。如果這沒有解決問題，"
"請到 Wacom 數位板設定中停用「雙響間距」。"

#: ../../contributors_manual/user_support.rst:64
msgid ""
"*XP-Pen tablets, pressure being uneven:* either switch to Windows 8+ Pointer "
"(Windows Ink) in :menuselection:`Configure Krita --> Tablet Settings`, or "
"disable Windows Ink in XP-Pen settings."
msgstr ""
"*XP-Pen 數位板筆壓不平均：*\\ 可嘗試在\\ :menuselection:`設定 Krita… --> 數位板設定`\\ 中切換至「"
"Windows 8+ 指標輸入 (Windows Ink)」，或到 XP-Pen 驅動程式設定中停用「Windows Ink」。"

#: ../../contributors_manual/user_support.rst:68
msgid "Gathering information"
msgstr "收集資料"

#: ../../contributors_manual/user_support.rst:70
msgid "Which OS do you use?"
msgstr "你使用哪個作業系統？"

#: ../../contributors_manual/user_support.rst:72
msgid "Which tablet do you have?"
msgstr "你使用甚麼品牌和型號的數位板？"

#: ../../contributors_manual/user_support.rst:74
msgid "What is the version of the tablet driver?"
msgstr "你裝有的數位板驅動程式版本編號是甚麼？"

#: ../../contributors_manual/user_support.rst:76
msgid ""
"Please collect Tablet Tester (:menuselection:`Configure Krita --> Tablet "
"Settings --> Tablet Tester``) text output and share it: :ref:"
"`intro_user_support_sharing_files`."
msgstr ""
"請收集數位板測試器（\\ :menuselection:`設定 Krita… --> 數位板設定 --> 開啟數位板測試器`\\ "
"）中的文字輸出並提供予支援者：\\ :ref:`intro_user_support_sharing_files`\\ 。"

#: ../../contributors_manual/user_support.rst:78
msgid "More detailed Tablet Events log:"
msgstr "收集更詳細的數位板事件紀錄："

#: ../../contributors_manual/user_support.rst:80
msgid ""
"Go to :menuselection:`Settings --> Dockers --> Log Viewer` docker, make sure "
"it's checked."
msgstr "開啟\\ :menuselection:`設定 --> 工具面板 --> 紀錄檢視器`\\ 工具面板，確認已勾選該選項。"

#: ../../contributors_manual/user_support.rst:82
msgid ""
"In the Log Viewer docker, make sure the first button is pressed (which means "
"the logging is turned on)."
msgstr "在「紀錄檢視器」工具面板中，確認第一個開關按鈕「啟用紀錄」處於按下狀態（即已啟用記錄事件）。"

#: ../../contributors_manual/user_support.rst:84
msgid "Press :kbd:`Ctrl + Shift + T` to turn on tablet events logging."
msgstr "按下 :kbd:`Ctrl + Shift + T` 以啟用數位板事件紀錄。"

#: ../../contributors_manual/user_support.rst:86
msgid ""
"Make a few strokes (depending on the situation, the user supporter or "
"developer can ask you for specific series of strokes)."
msgstr "畫出數道筆跡（按情況需求，支援者或開發者可要求作出特定的筆跡動作）。"

#: ../../contributors_manual/user_support.rst:88
msgid ""
"Press :kbd:`Ctrl + Shift + T` to turn off the logging of the tablet events."
msgstr "按下 :kbd:`Ctrl + Shift + T` 以停用數位板事件紀錄。"

#: ../../contributors_manual/user_support.rst:90
msgid ""
"Press the third button in the Log Viewer to save the output into a file."
msgstr "在「紀錄檢視器」工具面板中點選第三個按鈕以儲存紀錄到檔案。"

#: ../../contributors_manual/user_support.rst:92
msgid ""
"Share the file or share the content of the file: :ref:"
"`intro_user_support_sharing_files`."
msgstr "將檔案或檔案內容提供予支援者：\\ :ref:`intro_user_support_sharing_files`\\ 。"

#: ../../contributors_manual/user_support.rst:94
msgid ""
"On Linux, you can just use a console instead of Log Viewer -- then you'd "
"only need to enable tablet events logging, not logging in general."
msgstr "使用 Linux 的話可以直接從主控台視窗取得紀錄內容。這樣只需要啟用數位板事件紀錄，可以跳過「紀錄檢視器」工具面板。"

#: ../../contributors_manual/user_support.rst:100
msgid "Additional information for supporters"
msgstr "給支援者的額外資訊"

#: ../../contributors_manual/user_support.rst:102
msgid ""
"Except for the issue with beginnings of the strokes, Wacom tablets usually "
"work no matter the OS."
msgstr "除了起筆時出現直線線段的問題之外，Wacom 數位板通常都能在各個作業系統上正常運作。"

#: ../../contributors_manual/user_support.rst:104
msgid ""
"Huion tablets should work on Windows and on Linux, on macOS there might be "
"issues."
msgstr "繪王 (Huion) 數位板在 Windows 和 Linux 上應該能正常運作，但在 macOS 上可能會有問題。"

#: ../../contributors_manual/user_support.rst:106
msgid ""
"XP-Pen tablets and the rest of brands can have issues everywhere (on all "
"systems)."
msgstr "XP-Pen 以及其他品牌的數位板在各個作業系統上都可能會有各種問題。"

#: ../../contributors_manual/user_support.rst:108
msgid ""
"If someone asks about a tablet to buy, generally a cheaper Wacom or a Huion "
"are the best options as of 2019, if they want to work with Krita. :ref:"
"`list_supported_tablets`."
msgstr ""
"有關選擇數位板的建議，針對與 Krita 使用的話，一般來說一塊較便宜的 Wacom 或 Huion 數位板會是較好的選擇（2019 年計）。可參見\\ "
":ref:`list_supported_tablets`\\ 。"

#: ../../contributors_manual/user_support.rst:110
msgid ""
"`Possibly useful instruction in case of XP-Pen tablet issues <https://www."
"reddit.com/r/krita/comments/btzh72/"
"xppen_artist_12s_issue_with_krita_how_to_fix_it/>`_."
msgstr ""
"`對於 XP-Pen 數位板出現的問題，這裡的指示可能會有幫助 <https://www.reddit.com/r/krita/comments/"
"btzh72/xppen_artist_12s_issue_with_krita_how_to_fix_it/>`_\\ 。"

#: ../../contributors_manual/user_support.rst:114
msgid "Animation"
msgstr "動畫"

#: ../../contributors_manual/user_support.rst:116
msgid ""
"Issues with rendering animation can be of various shapes and colors. First "
"thing to find out is whether the issue happens on Krita's or FFmpeg's side "
"(Krita saves all the frames, then FFmpeg is used to render a video using "
"this sequence of images). To learn that, instruct the user to render as "
"\"Image Sequence\". If the image sequence is correct, FFmpeg (or more often: "
"render options) are at fault. If the image sequence is incorrect, either the "
"options are wrong (if for example not every frame got rendered), or it's a "
"bug in Krita."
msgstr ""
"與動畫繪製輸出相關的問題可以是各式各樣的。首要步驟是查出問題根源是在 Krita 內部還是 FFmpeg 方面（Krita 先輸出所有影格，然後 "
"FFmpeg 用這影像序列產生影片檔案）。為找出答案，請指示使用者將動畫繪製匯出為「影像序列」。如影像序列輸出正確無誤，這表示是 FFmpeg "
"或者繪製選項（後者較常見）出現問題。如影像序列輸出不正確，有機會是一般選項出錯（例如沒有繪製所有影格），又或者是 Krita 有程式錯誤。"

#: ../../contributors_manual/user_support.rst:120
msgid ""
"If the user opens the Log Viewer docker, turns on logging and then tries to "
"render a video, Krita will print out the whole ffmpeg command to Log Viewer "
"so it can be easily investigated."
msgstr ""
"如使用者開啟「紀錄檢視器」工具面板並啟用紀錄，然後嘗試繪製動畫影片輸出，Krita 會將整句 ffmpeg 命令列輸出到「紀錄檢視器」之內供調查用。"

#: ../../contributors_manual/user_support.rst:122
msgid ""
"There is a log file called *log_encode.log* in the directory that user tries "
"to render to. It can contain information useful to investigation of the "
"issue (sharing files: :ref:`intro_user_support_sharing_files`)."
msgstr ""
"在繪製動畫的輸出目錄內會有一個名為「log_encode.log」的紀錄檔。這個檔案包含了對調查問題有幫肋的資訊（請參見\\ "
":ref:`intro_user_support_sharing_files`\\ ）。"

#: ../../contributors_manual/user_support.rst:125
msgid "Onion skin issues"
msgstr "洋蔥皮相關問題"

#: ../../contributors_manual/user_support.rst:127
msgid ""
"The great majority of issues with onion skin are just user errors, not bugs. "
"Nonetheless, you need to find out why it happens and direct the user how to "
"use onion skin properly."
msgstr ""
"絕大部份與洋蔥皮相關的問題都是使用者操作不當，而不是程式的問題。儘管如此，找出問題發生的原因，還有是指導使用者正確使用洋蔥皮，都是提供技術支援要做的工作。"

#: ../../contributors_manual/user_support.rst:131
msgid "Crash"
msgstr "軟體崩潰"

#: ../../contributors_manual/user_support.rst:133
msgid ""
"In case of crash try to determine if the problem is known, if not, instruct "
"user to create a bug report (or create it yourself) with following "
"information:"
msgstr ""
"如遇到程式強制終止的情況，應嘗試判斷這是否已知的問題。假如不是，應指示使用者到 Bugzilla "
"建立一個缺陷報告，或者由支援者代為建立。缺陷報告內應含以下資訊："

#: ../../contributors_manual/user_support.rst:135
msgid "What happened, what was being done just before the crash."
msgstr "發生了甚麼事？程式強制終止前那一刻在做甚麼？"

#: ../../contributors_manual/user_support.rst:137
msgid ""
"Is it possible to reproduce (repeat)? If yes, provide a step-by-step "
"instruction to get the crash."
msgstr "能夠重現這個問題（使其重複發生）嗎？如可，請提供一系列可以重現這個問題的步驟。"

#: ../../contributors_manual/user_support.rst:139
msgid ""
"Backtrace (crashlog) -- the instruction for Windows is here: :ref:`dr_minw`, "
"and the debug symbols can be found in the annoucement of the version of "
"Krita that the user has. But it could be easier to just point the user to "
"`https://download.kde.org/stable/krita <https://download.kde.org/stable/"
"krita>`_."
msgstr ""
"Backtrace（當機紀錄）——給 Windows 使用者的指示在這裡：\\ :ref:`dr_minw`\\ "
"，而偵錯符號封裝的下載連結可在該版本的發佈新聞內找到，亦可直接在 `https://download.kde.org/stable/krita "
"<https://download.kde.org/stable/krita>`_ 裡面找到。"

#: ../../contributors_manual/user_support.rst:143
msgid "Other possible questions with quick solutions"
msgstr "其他可能有快捷解決方法的問題"

#: ../../contributors_manual/user_support.rst:145
msgid ""
"When the user has any weird issue, something you've never heard about, ask "
"them to reset the configuration: :ref:`faq_reset_krita_configuration`."
msgstr ""
"如使用者遇到任何未聽聞過的奇怪的問題，請要求該使用者先嘗試\\ :ref:`重設 Krita 的設定選項 "
"<faq_reset_krita_configuration>`\\ 。"

#: ../../contributors_manual/user_support.rst:147
msgid ""
"When the user on Windows has trouble with anything related to preview or "
"display, ask them to change :guilabel:`Canvas Graphics Acceleration` in :"
"menuselection:`Settings --> Configure Krita --> Display`."
msgstr ""
"如有 Windows 的使用者遇到任何與畫布顯示有關的問題，請要求該使用者嘗試更改\\ :menuselection:`設定 --> 設定 Krita… "
"--> 顯示`\\ 內\\ :guilabel:`畫布圖形加速`\\ 的「繪製器」設定。"

#: ../../contributors_manual/user_support.rst:151
msgid ""
"Telling people to disable canvas acceleration to get better performance is "
"something we shouldn't do, ever."
msgstr "在任何情況下都不應建議使用者停用「畫布圖形加速」來改善效能。"

#: ../../contributors_manual/user_support.rst:155
msgid "Advices for supporters"
msgstr "給支援者的忠告"

#: ../../contributors_manual/user_support.rst:157
msgid ""
"If you don't understand the question, ask for clarification -- asking for a "
"screen recording or a screenshot is perfectly fine."
msgstr "如果未能清楚理解求助者的提問，應請求闡明一下。要求提供畫面截圖或錄影是不錯的做法。"

#: ../../contributors_manual/user_support.rst:159
msgid ""
"If you don't know the solution but you know what information will be needed "
"to investigate the issue further, don't hesitate to ask. Other supporters "
"may know the answer, but have too little time to move the user through the "
"whole process, so you're helping a lot just by asking for additional "
"information. This is very much true in case of tablet issues, for example."
msgstr ""
"如果不知道解決方法，但知道調查問題需要甚麼額外資訊的話，可以先向求助者查詢。這樣可以幫助其他知道解決方法的支援者更快能夠提供進一步支援。這尤其適用於與數位"
"板有關的問題。"

#: ../../contributors_manual/user_support.rst:161
msgid ""
"If you don't know the answer/solution and the question looks abandoned by "
"other supporters, you can always ask for help on Krita IRC channel. It's "
"#krita on Libera.Chat: :ref:`the_krita_community`."
msgstr ""
"如果不知道答案或解決方法而問題看來被其他支援者忽視，不妨到 Krita 的 IRC 聊天室提問（Libera.Chat 上的 #krita）：\\ "
":ref:`the_krita_community`\\ 。"

#: ../../contributors_manual/user_support.rst:163
msgid ""
"Explain steps the user needs to make clearly, for example if you need them "
"to change something in settings, clearly state the whole path of buttons and "
"tabs to get there."
msgstr "向使用者清楚解釋他應採取的步驟。例如要修改某項設定的話，應完整列出每個步驟要點選的按鈕、選單與分頁。"

#: ../../contributors_manual/user_support.rst:165
msgid ""
"Instead of :menuselection:`Settings --> Configure Krita...` use just :"
"menuselection:`Configure Krita` -- it's easy enough to find and macOS users "
"(where you need to select :menuselection:`Krita --> Preferences...`) won't "
"get confused."
msgstr ""
"不要寫\\ :menuselection:`設定 --> 設定 Krita…`\\ ，只需要寫\\ :menuselection:`設定 Krita`\\"
" ——這個選單項目容易找到，而且這樣寫不會使 macOS 使用者產生混淆（因為在 macOS 上要經由\\ :menuselection:`Krita "
"--> 偏好設定...`\\ 才能開啟設定）。"

#: ../../contributors_manual/user_support.rst:167
msgid ""
"If you ask for an image, mention usage of `Imgur <https://imgur.com>`_ or "
"`Pasteboard <https://pasteboard.co>`_ (:ref:"
"`intro_user_support_sharing_files`), otherwise Reddit users might create a "
"new post with this image instead of including it to the old conversation."
msgstr ""
"如要求求助者提供影像，可建議 `Imgur <https://imgur.com>`_ 或 `Pasteboard <https://pasteboard"
".co>`_\\ （\\ :ref:`intro_user_support_sharing_files`\\ ），否則 Reddit "
"使用者可能會用該影像發表一篇新貼文而非從原本的討論串連結到該影像。"

#: ../../contributors_manual/user_support.rst:169
msgid ""
"If you want to quickly answer someone, just link to the appropriate place in "
"this manual page -- you can click on the little link icon next to the "
"section or subsection title and give the link to the user so they for "
"example know what information about their tablet issue you need."
msgstr "快捷回答：如本說明文件內有相關內容，可直接連結到說明文件中相應的頁面。點擊章節標題旁的連結圖示即可複製連結，以提供予求助者作參考。"

#: ../../contributors_manual/user_support.rst:176
msgid "How to share a file"
msgstr "如何分享檔案"

#: ../../contributors_manual/user_support.rst:179
msgid ""
"Images (e.g. screenshots): `Imgur <https://imgur.com>`_ [*], `Pasteboard "
"<https://pasteboard.co>`_"
msgstr ""
"影像（例如畫面截圖）：\\ `Imgur <https://imgur.com>`_ [*]、\\ `Pasteboard "
"<https://pasteboard.co>`_"

#: ../../contributors_manual/user_support.rst:181
msgid ""
"Text only: `Pastebin <https://pastebin.com>`_ [*], `BPaste <https://bpaste."
"net>`_, `paste.ubuntu.org.cn <https://paste.ubuntu.org.cn>`_, `CentOS's "
"Pastebin Service <https://paste.centos.org/>`_ or `KDE Snippets (needs KDE "
"Identity) <https://invent.kde.org/dashboard/snippets>`_."
msgstr ""
"純文字：\\ `Pastebin <https://pastebin.com>`_ [*]、\\ `BPaste <https://bpaste."
"net>`_、\\ `paste.ubuntu.org.cn <https://paste.ubuntu.org.cn>`_\\ 、\\ `CentOS "
"的 Pastebin 服務 <https://paste.centos.org/>`_\\ 、\\ `KDE Snippets（需要 KDE "
"Identity） <https://invent.kde.org/dashboard/snippets>`_"

#: ../../contributors_manual/user_support.rst:183
msgid ""
"``.kra`` and other formats: by mail? Or encode the file using *base64* "
"command on Linux, send by mail or on Pastebin, then decode using the same "
"command."
msgstr ""
"``.kra`` 以及其他檔案格式：電子郵件。或可以經 Linux 提供的 *base64* 命令列工具編碼並放到純文字分享服務，然後用相同的工具解碼。"

#: ../../contributors_manual/user_support.rst:190
msgid ""
"If you ask user to store their log or other data on a website, make sure it "
"stays there long enough for you to get it -- for example bpaste.net stores "
"files by default only for a day! And you can extend it only to one week."
msgstr ""
"如果要求求助者經純文字分享服務提供紀錄或其他資料，請確保這些資料的保存時長足夠讓你存取並下載——例如 bpaste.net "
"網站預設只會將檔案保存一天，而最長只可延長到保存一個星期。"

